titles.title: A bill to designate the Federal building located at 131 East 4th Street in Davenport, Iowa, as the "James A. Leach Federal Building".

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Environment and Public Works.

bill.summary:
3/13/2007--Introduced.
Designates the federal building located at 131 East 4th Street in Davenport, Iowa, as the "James A. Leach Federal Building."
